In order to compile the program the user needs to perform the following steps:

1) open "configure" file and set the following system-specific variables:
   SDK_COMMON_DIR
   SDK_COMMON_LIB_DIR
   TOOLKIT_INC_DIR
   ARCH

2) run commands:
   ./configure
   make

Launching the program: ./gpas
                       ./gpas --help
                       ./gpas --version

